Additional Downloads
You will need to install GNAT temporarily to satisfy the circular dependency. You may point your browser to the AdaCore download page, choose your platform and 2017 (64 bit machines) or 2014 (32 bit machines), then select the file to download. Alternatively, direct links to the 64 bit and 32 bit linux versions are given below.
